<dl id="n12062e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12062e">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12062e"> 62(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> washing his suit he / must lie abed</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Semblables aux messieurs les gentilshommes de Plouescat / Doivent rester au lit quand on nettoie leurs v&ecirc;tements. <br><font color="green">[Just like those gentlemen in Plouescat, who have to stay in bed while their clothes are being cleaned]</font> <small> L-F. Sauv&eacute, <a name="LFSP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#LFSP"><cite title="source">Proverbes et dictons de la Basse-Bretagne</cite></a> (1878) 155</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
